Attachments
precis:
Authority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to make a payment from the separate
account referred to in subsection 39(2) of the Act to the CANADIAN
INTERNATIONAL GRAINS INSTITUTE in order to defray some of its capital costs
during the period commencing on August 1, 1991 and ending on July 31, 1995.
